WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.070
Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:06.070
Thank you for joining us. What a blessing!

00:00:06.080 --> 00:00:07.389
We have some things we're going

00:00:07.399 --> 00:00:09.030
to pray about. First off, I just want to

00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:10.990
tell you all thank you for all your

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:13.110
support, for all the likes, the shares, the

00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:16.189
comments down below, and the emails.

00:00:16.199 --> 00:00:17.710
We've been praying for all the things

00:00:17.720 --> 00:00:20.189
you've been sending us.

00:00:20.199 --> 00:00:21.550
There's a lot of you that are going

00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:24.390
through a lot, and Diana and I truly

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:28.269
pray for you. We love you. We agree

00:00:28.279 --> 00:00:30.589
by faith that God is meeting you at

00:00:30.599 --> 00:00:33.030
the point of your need; that everything

00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:34.790
that you're ever believing for, what

00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:38.510
you're asking for, all of it, God has it.

00:00:38.520 --> 00:00:40.910
I believe this is going to be a good

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:42.630
year for you.

00:00:42.640 --> 00:00:46.029
2025 will be a year you thrive. A

00:00:46.039 --> 00:00:49.069
supernatural abundant supply is coming

00:00:49.079 --> 00:00:54.189
to you. We see right now the SEC saying

00:00:54.199 --> 00:00:56.549
that they want to drop the case against

00:00:56.559 --> 00:01:01.069
XRP in the days ahead. I saw an article,

00:01:01.079 --> 00:01:03.590
so we're praying. That's what we've been

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:05.830
praying for. We've been praying for the

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:07.950
wealth of the sinner laid up

00:01:07.960 --> 00:01:09.710
for the righteous and the wealth

00:01:09.720 --> 00:01:13.990
transfer. I believe the wealth transfer

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:16.310
goes hand-in-hand with the great revival

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:18.990
that's about to take place. We will see

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:20.190
one of the

00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:23.390
greatest revivals this world has ever

00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:25.670
had. When I

00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:27.270
was driving down the

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:31.230
road on Sunday, I looked over and

00:01:31.240 --> 00:01:34.950
I saw a Methodist church on a hill.

00:01:36.479 --> 00:01:38.429
Instantaneously, I started seeing in

00:01:38.439 --> 00:01:40.990
the spirit when I was praying. I saw

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:45.789
a storm coming.

00:01:45.799 --> 00:01:48.709
I saw the doves flying down and doing

00:01:48.719 --> 00:01:50.910
that circular motion. Remember

00:01:50.920 --> 00:01:52.870
I told you all I saw the doves and they

00:01:52.880 --> 00:01:54.950
were coming out of this

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:57.590
bright light when I was praying?

00:01:57.600 --> 00:01:59.029
Then all of a sudden they started

00:01:59.039 --> 00:02:01.990
twirling and then

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:04.230
they exploded, but they went all over the

00:02:04.240 --> 00:02:06.830
four corners of the Earth, all around the

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:08.389
world.

00:02:08.399 --> 00:02:11.150
They went to all the continents.

00:02:11.160 --> 00:02:15.309
I believe again

00:02:15.319 --> 00:02:17.309
I saw those doves circling and the Lord

00:02:17.319 --> 00:02:20.350
told me, 'Brandon, I want you to

00:02:20.360 --> 00:02:22.509
pray for

00:02:22.519 --> 00:02:25.309
Easter. I want you to intercede for

00:02:25.319 --> 00:02:27.830
Easter and what's about to take place,

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:31.190
for a great manifestation of my

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:33.869
presence is upon my people.'I've told

00:02:33.879 --> 00:02:36.910
you all, what's the tipping point? What is

00:02:36.920 --> 00:02:39.430
it that we're waiting for? What is it

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:42.630
that's going to thrust this thing into

00:02:42.640 --> 00:02:43.550
full

00:02:43.560 --> 00:02:45.550
gear? That's what I've been interceding

00:02:45.550 --> 00:02:45.560
for, Diana

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:47.790
and I both. We've been

00:02:47.800 --> 00:02:49.910
just stirring ourselves up. How do you stay

00:02:49.910 --> 00:02:49.920
to the point of

00:02:49.920 --> 00:02:52.910
being filled?

00:02:52.920 --> 00:02:55.190
I wanted to

00:02:55.200 --> 00:02:56.990
study Katherine

00:02:56.990 --> 00:02:57.000
Kuhlman

00:02:57.000 --> 00:02:59.589
because I was like,

00:02:59.599 --> 00:03:02.550
'What was the secret? How did she walk in

00:03:02.560 --> 00:03:05.030
what she walked

00:03:05.030 --> 00:03:05.040
in?'Billy

00:03:05.040 --> 00:03:07.110
Burke is somebody that I follow a

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:09.750
lot. I love Billy Burke, but he talks

00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:13.030
about being filled all the time. Does he

00:03:13.040 --> 00:03:15.350
pray a lot before his services?

00:03:20.080 --> 00:03:23.670
No, he stays filled all day long. I

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:25.949
thought, 'How do you do

00:03:25.949 --> 00:03:25.959
that?'You

00:03:25.959 --> 00:03:28.789
practice His presence. Billy

00:03:28.789 --> 00:03:28.799
Burke

00:03:28.799 --> 00:03:30.750
practices His presence. He sent me this,

00:03:30.760 --> 00:03:32.149
by the way, which I thought was so

00:03:32.159 --> 00:03:34.470
awesome; he sent me this

00:03:34.480 --> 00:03:37.070
anointing oil that has frankincense in

00:03:37.080 --> 00:03:39.789
it. What a blessing.

00:03:39.799 --> 00:03:41.270
There's a lot of you all that have been

00:03:41.280 --> 00:03:43.429
going to his meetings

00:03:43.429 --> 00:03:43.439
in

00:03:43.439 --> 00:03:46.070
Pittsburgh.

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:48.190
You all are so kind

00:03:48.190 --> 00:03:48.200
to

00:03:48.200 --> 00:03:49.710
bring up my name; you don't have to do

00:03:49.720 --> 00:03:52.309
that. It's such a blessing that you all

00:03:52.319 --> 00:03:54.429
would go and support him. I pray that

00:03:54.439 --> 00:03:56.030
you're getting richly blessed when you

00:03:56.040 --> 00:03:58.750
go. Every time I go

00:03:58.760 --> 00:04:00.429
to a Billy Burke

00:04:00.429 --> 00:04:00.439
meeting,

00:04:00.439 --> 00:04:03.630
it is a treasure going into his

00:04:03.640 --> 00:04:05.910
presence, just sitting there

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:09.509
in the meetings. It's

00:04:09.519 --> 00:04:11.589
tremendous. It's life-changing,

00:04:11.599 --> 00:04:14.750
isn't it, baby? All you need is one second

00:04:14.760 --> 00:04:17.069
in His presence and you'll be forever

00:04:17.079 --> 00:04:19.110
changed. It's not that Billy Burke is—well, it's not all about Billy Burke, folks. Billy

00:04:19.120 --> 00:04:21.949
Burke is

00:04:21.959 --> 00:04:24.189
a

00:04:24.199 --> 00:04:26.749
carrier and he practices the presence

00:04:26.759 --> 00:04:28.830
just like every single one of us. God's

00:04:28.840 --> 00:04:30.790
not favoring Billy Burke any more than

00:04:30.800 --> 00:04:32.950
He'll do something with you. Billy

00:04:32.960 --> 00:04:35.870
Burke's just taken 50 years to cultivate

00:04:35.880 --> 00:04:38.350
something inside of his life, of being

00:04:38.360 --> 00:04:41.749
dedicated to sitting at Jesus's feet.

00:04:41.759 --> 00:04:44.870
If you do that, God will use you.

00:04:44.880 --> 00:04:46.710
That's why Diana and I are

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:50.469
hungry. If you can go to

00:04:50.479 --> 00:04:52.710
where the water is at, you can have a

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:55.790
drink. If you can get to where

00:04:55.800 --> 00:04:57.670
the water and the flow of the Holy

00:04:57.680 --> 00:05:00.430
Spirit's at, you can get a drink.

00:05:00.440 --> 00:05:02.550
But if you're going where

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:04.950
it's dry, you have to stir

00:05:04.960 --> 00:05:06.790
yourself up like we were doing

00:05:06.800 --> 00:05:09.390
yesterday,

00:05:09.400 --> 00:05:12.749
praying for the dryness. I

00:05:12.759 --> 00:05:15.270
saw great dryness in Amarillo and all around

00:05:15.280 --> 00:05:17.590
the area, and the Lord said, 'I'm bringing

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:18.469
a

00:05:18.479 --> 00:05:22.309
rain. I'm going to bring a fresh

00:05:22.309 --> 00:05:22.319
rain.'Then

00:05:22.319 --> 00:05:25.430
I saw the Body of Christ floating

00:05:25.440 --> 00:05:27.990
down the river, enjoying themselves as a

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:30.350
family. That

00:05:30.360 --> 00:05:32.230
might be something people

00:05:32.240 --> 00:05:34.590
in the South do,

00:05:34.600 --> 00:05:37.029
go tubing, but there's

00:05:37.039 --> 00:05:39.070
a lot of memories

00:05:39.080 --> 00:05:42.710
made on the river. Getting in

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:45.029
the river, getting in the flow of the

00:05:45.039 --> 00:05:47.830
Holy Ghost, and then fanning

00:05:47.830 --> 00:05:47.840
that flame—you

00:05:47.840 --> 00:05:50.270
don't walk away unchanged. You

00:05:50.280 --> 00:05:53.670
fan it and fan it and

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:55.629
you walk away and you bring it home with

00:05:55.639 --> 00:05:59.990
you and you live there.

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:01.830
It's not a place to

00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:03.950
visit. Don't dry out once you get there.

00:06:03.960 --> 00:06:05.830
Don't let it die.

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:07.870
It takes us doing it

00:06:07.880 --> 00:06:09.710
because here we are.

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:11.550
We went to his meeting and we're so

00:06:11.560 --> 00:06:13.029
excited, but then you get away from it and you

00:06:13.029 --> 00:06:13.039
ask,

00:06:13.039 --> 00:06:15.830
'How do you keep that

00:06:15.840 --> 00:06:17.469
fire going?'You've got that fire

00:06:17.479 --> 00:06:19.189
going inside of you and

00:06:19.199 --> 00:06:20.990
you're excited and radical,

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:23.390
but

00:06:23.400 --> 00:06:25.430
then you have your

00:06:25.440 --> 00:06:27.830
day-to-day life. You go back to eBay,

00:06:27.840 --> 00:06:30.029
Poshmark, listing things,

00:06:30.039 --> 00:06:31.510
going to thrift stores, pressing

00:06:31.520 --> 00:06:32.830
through life, getting kids

00:06:32.840 --> 00:06:34.830
through school.

00:06:34.840 --> 00:06:36.670
All the

00:06:36.680 --> 00:06:38.870
things of life try to put that out because

00:06:38.880 --> 00:06:42.230
you're always leaking out.

00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:43.830
The lady at the grocery store was rude

00:06:43.840 --> 00:06:45.589
to you, maybe somebody at church was rude

00:06:45.599 --> 00:06:46.909
to you.

00:06:51.560 --> 00:06:53.110
The devil comes to try to

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:54.790
distract you and try to make you upset.

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:56.230
They always say if the

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:58.510
devil can't get you, he'll keep you busy.

00:07:00.479 --> 00:07:02.749
That's exactly what he does; he tries to

00:07:02.759 --> 00:07:05.629
keep you chasing your tail. If he

00:07:05.639 --> 00:07:08.309
can keep you that way, then

00:07:08.319 --> 00:07:09.790
you'll go through your day and

00:07:09.790 --> 00:07:09.800
wonder

00:07:09.800 --> 00:07:12.150
what

00:07:12.150 --> 00:07:12.160
you

00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:13.749
did today.

00:07:13.759 --> 00:07:16.029
You didn't

00:07:16.039 --> 00:07:18.830
take the time sitting at His feet.

00:07:18.840 --> 00:07:21.189
The Lord spoke to me the other day and

00:07:21.199 --> 00:07:24.029
he said, 'The lengths that I require are not

00:07:24.039 --> 00:07:26.990
old, tired days. The lengths that I require

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:29.909
are the new, fresh days out of the new

00:07:29.909 --> 00:07:29.919
wineskin.'Not

00:07:29.919 --> 00:07:34.950
giving

00:07:34.960 --> 00:07:36.869
Him the last, but giving Him the first.

00:07:36.879 --> 00:07:39.230
Giving Him priority,

00:07:39.240 --> 00:07:41.749
fanning the flame, and putting Him

00:07:41.749 --> 00:07:41.759
first—those

00:07:41.759 --> 00:07:43.950
are all ways you practice

00:07:43.960 --> 00:07:46.710
His presence. Not giving Him

00:07:46.720 --> 00:07:50.070
leftovers. 'God, I'm tired, but

00:07:50.080 --> 00:07:51.830
I'll give you a couple of minutes before

00:07:51.840 --> 00:07:54.950
I go to bed,'which is better than

00:07:54.960 --> 00:07:58.469
nothing, but it's

00:07:58.469 --> 00:07:58.479
about

00:07:58.479 --> 00:08:00.950
making Him first place in your

00:08:00.960 --> 00:08:03.670
life and saying, 'Father, I need you

00:08:03.680 --> 00:08:06.710
today. When my feet hit

00:08:06.720 --> 00:08:07.510
the

00:08:07.520 --> 00:08:10.710
ground, God, I need you today.'Even

00:08:10.710 --> 00:08:10.720
when

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:12.430
Billy Burke was talking

00:08:12.440 --> 00:08:14.270
about saying, 'I just need you. I need

00:08:14.280 --> 00:08:16.830
you today in this life. Holy Spirit, fill

00:08:16.840 --> 00:08:19.749
me. I need a fresh drink of your living

00:08:19.759 --> 00:08:23.029
water today. I'm desperate for you. Fill

00:08:23.029 --> 00:08:23.039
me.'The

00:08:23.039 --> 00:08:26.830
more you practice His

00:08:26.840 --> 00:08:28.909
presence... I want to sit

00:08:28.919 --> 00:08:30.350
outside.

00:08:30.360 --> 00:08:31.909
I like to see

00:08:31.919 --> 00:08:34.350
nature. I love the

00:08:36.680 --> 00:08:40.469
beauty of nature and I

00:08:40.479 --> 00:08:43.630
see Him in it.

00:08:43.640 --> 00:08:46.230
People say, 'Well,

00:08:46.240 --> 00:08:47.949
you know, evolution and all this

00:08:47.949 --> 00:08:47.959
stuff.'I

00:08:47.959 --> 00:08:49.710
think, how in the world could you

00:08:49.720 --> 00:08:52.030
believe in evolution if you sit

00:08:52.040 --> 00:08:53.949
outside for ten minutes and just look at

00:08:53.959 --> 00:08:56.269
the stuff that God created? There's

00:08:56.279 --> 00:08:58.829
no way that a tree went from an oak tree to

00:08:58.839 --> 00:09:01.550
a pine tree to a sycamore tree.

00:09:03.720 --> 00:09:07.389
I can't even

00:09:07.399 --> 00:09:09.110
fathom that.

00:09:10.920 --> 00:09:13.069
We have two

00:09:13.079 --> 00:09:15.190
eagles that fly around our

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:19.870
house, and it's amazing how majestic

00:09:19.880 --> 00:09:22.870
an eagle is. Diana

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:26.470
found this... I was thinking

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:30.350
about all the trials that we face as

00:09:30.360 --> 00:09:33.710
believers and we get

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:36.990
discouraged when we don't see the

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:39.230
full manifestation of what we're going

00:09:39.240 --> 00:09:43.110
through. You get to that point of

00:09:43.120 --> 00:09:45.509
desperation, and I see it in so many

00:09:45.519 --> 00:09:47.670
of your letters.

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:52.750
Whenever you get frustrated and you get

00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:55.350
weary in well-doing and you get annoyed at

00:09:55.360 --> 00:09:57.550
your circumstance, you

00:09:57.550 --> 00:09:57.560
have

00:09:57.560 --> 00:09:59.949
a tendency

00:10:02.230 --> 00:10:02.240
to

00:10:06.640 --> 00:10:08.870
start blaming

00:10:08.880 --> 00:10:11.750
God. 'Why am I still living this?'We hear

00:10:11.760 --> 00:10:15.550
so much in things past that you

00:10:15.560 --> 00:10:18.750
didn't have enough faith to be healed. I

00:10:18.760 --> 00:10:20.590
can't tell you how many times I've been

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:21.829
told that about

00:10:21.839 --> 00:10:24.990
Megan. People say, 'Well, there's a devil; it's because

00:10:25.000 --> 00:10:27.910
you opened the door through sin, brother.

00:10:30.440 --> 00:10:32.509
I believe there must have

00:10:32.519 --> 00:10:34.750
been sin in your life for this to have

00:10:36.910 --> 00:10:36.920
happened.'I'm

00:10:42.079 --> 00:10:44.550
telling you, you want

00:10:44.560 --> 00:10:46.190
to deck them in the face when they go

00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:48.350
off like that.

00:10:49.880 --> 00:10:53.110
I'm just being real

00:10:53.120 --> 00:10:54.790
because there's been people that

00:10:54.800 --> 00:10:57.150
just try to figure it

00:10:57.160 --> 00:11:00.910
out. I love

00:11:00.920 --> 00:11:02.949
when Billy Burke said this. He

00:11:02.949 --> 00:11:02.959
asked

00:11:02.959 --> 00:11:05.670
Katherine

00:11:05.670 --> 00:11:05.680
Kuhlman

00:11:05.680 --> 00:11:07.910
a question and

00:11:07.920 --> 00:11:12.190
she said, 'I don't

00:11:12.190 --> 00:11:12.200
know.'She

00:11:12.200 --> 00:11:16.350
told

00:11:16.360 --> 00:11:18.670
Billy,

00:11:18.680 --> 00:11:22.350
'Learn three words, Billy, and

00:11:22.360 --> 00:11:23.590
this will help you all the way through

00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:28.350
your ministry: I don't

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:29.750
know.'I

00:11:29.760 --> 00:11:31.590
don't know why you go through

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:33.269
some of the stuff you're going through.

00:11:33.279 --> 00:11:35.750
I don't know why you're

00:11:35.760 --> 00:11:39.670
not healed yet. I don't know why you're

00:11:39.680 --> 00:11:41.389
still believing for it, like I'm still

00:11:41.399 --> 00:11:43.629
believing for mine year after year. You

00:11:43.639 --> 00:11:45.110
go through healing line after healing line

00:11:45.120 --> 00:11:46.470
and you're still believing for

00:11:46.480 --> 00:11:48.870
the manifestation. You get

00:11:48.880 --> 00:11:51.829
weary after a while and you say

00:11:51.829 --> 00:11:51.839
to yourself,

00:11:51.839 --> 00:11:54.069
'God, are you

00:11:55.880 --> 00:11:58.150
there?'Was

00:12:01.200 --> 00:12:03.670
it a lack of faith?

00:12:09.040 --> 00:12:12.190
Did you not have enough

00:12:12.200 --> 00:12:14.310
heart after God? Did you not

00:12:14.320 --> 00:12:16.590
confess enough?

00:12:16.600 --> 00:12:19.949
You walk away

00:12:19.959 --> 00:12:24.150
defeated, feeling like

00:12:24.150 --> 00:12:24.160
you

00:12:24.160 --> 00:12:27.230
don't have what it takes.

00:12:27.240 --> 00:12:30.550
Am I the

00:12:30.560 --> 00:12:32.430
only one that ever walks away with that?

00:12:34.160 --> 00:12:36.910
You walk away feeling,

00:12:39.639 --> 00:12:42.389
'I just don't measure up

00:12:42.399 --> 00:12:44.949
because I didn't quote enough scripture,

00:12:44.959 --> 00:12:47.430
obviously, because I'm still

00:12:47.440 --> 00:12:49.430
getting over

00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:51.310
this and the doctor's giving me this

00:12:51.320 --> 00:12:54.230
report.'So

00:12:54.240 --> 00:12:56.949
I walk away saying,

00:12:56.959 --> 00:12:59.790
'Why do I even

00:12:59.800 --> 00:13:00.870
try?'There

00:13:00.880 --> 00:13:03.430
is a story in the

00:13:03.440 --> 00:13:06.829
Bible where Jesus told the

00:13:06.839 --> 00:13:08.990
disciples, when

00:13:08.990 --> 00:13:09.000
they

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:10.550
asked if

00:13:10.550 --> 00:13:10.560
it

00:13:10.560 --> 00:13:12.670
was because this

00:13:12.680 --> 00:13:14.269
family was in sin that this happened, Jesus said, 'No, it was so that the glory of God would be made known.'It wasn't that they sinned. It wasn't that the blind child was under judgment. It was at that

00:13:14.269 --> 00:13:14.279
moment that the glory of God would be known. So it's not always a

00:13:14.279 --> 00:13:15.949
sin door, or he would have

00:13:15.949 --> 00:13:15.959
said it to the disciples then.

00:13:15.959 --> 00:13:18.230
Jesus never said her daddy was committing adultery or he was out smoking or drinking. He said

00:13:18.240 --> 00:13:20.509
it was that at that moment the glory of God would

00:13:20.519 --> 00:13:22.150
be made

00:13:22.160 --> 00:13:24.870
known.

00:14:03.199 --> 00:14:06.629
I had to take that for me

00:14:06.639 --> 00:14:08.150
because I've gone to

00:14:08.160 --> 00:14:11.629
all the healing services,

00:14:11.639 --> 00:14:13.790
one after another,

00:14:13.800 --> 00:14:15.910
countless times. Fall out in the spirit, get

00:14:15.920 --> 00:14:19.389
up, and believe 'today's my

00:14:19.389 --> 00:14:19.399
day,'and

00:14:19.399 --> 00:14:22.470
you walk away feeling defeated when

00:14:22.480 --> 00:14:23.949
people say maybe you didn't have

00:14:23.959 --> 00:14:25.150
enough faith.

00:14:29.680 --> 00:14:33.310
I know it's easy to get weary in

00:14:33.310 --> 00:14:33.320
well-doing,

00:14:33.320 --> 00:14:36.430
but I always go back to

00:14:36.440 --> 00:14:38.910
the scripture: 'When there is

00:14:38.910 --> 00:14:38.920
nothing

00:14:38.920 --> 00:14:41.870
else to do, stand. Stand

00:14:41.870 --> 00:14:41.880
therefore.'I

00:14:41.880 --> 00:14:45.550
will stand regardless of the

00:14:45.560 --> 00:14:48.430
circumstance of

00:14:50.600 --> 00:14:53.670
what I see. I'm not moved by what I see; I'm

00:14:53.670 --> 00:14:53.680
not moved

00:14:53.680 --> 00:14:55.509
by what I feel; I'm moved by what the Word of God says.

00:14:55.519 --> 00:14:57.590
Diana found this

00:14:57.600 --> 00:15:00.030
little bit of a passage that Katherine

00:15:00.030 --> 00:15:00.040
Kuhlman

00:15:00.040 --> 00:15:02.470
said right here. I

00:15:04.519 --> 00:15:07.150
feel it's necessary for some of you to

00:15:07.160 --> 00:15:09.550
hear this because I see you at

00:15:09.560 --> 00:15:11.269
the point of

00:15:11.279 --> 00:15:13.550
desperation, and you don't see your

00:15:13.560 --> 00:15:15.829
miracle, and you're weary in well-doing. Diana

00:15:15.829 --> 00:15:15.839
and I live

00:15:15.839 --> 00:15:18.110
it

00:15:18.120 --> 00:15:21.790
too.

00:15:21.800 --> 00:15:24.189
You have people look at you

00:15:24.189 --> 00:15:24.199
with

00:15:24.199 --> 00:15:25.949
that

00:15:25.949 --> 00:15:25.959
'holier-than-thou'outlook.

00:15:25.959 --> 00:15:27.509
I

00:15:27.519 --> 00:15:30.309
was one of them. I

00:15:30.319 --> 00:15:32.910
looked across the table at a

00:15:32.920 --> 00:15:34.990
lady

00:15:34.990 --> 00:15:35.000
named

00:15:35.000 --> 00:15:38.389
Jane who was overcoming cancer,

00:15:38.399 --> 00:15:41.350
and I said, 'It's a mockery

00:15:41.350 --> 00:15:41.360
of

00:15:41.360 --> 00:15:43.470
the blood of Jesus for what He did

00:15:43.480 --> 00:15:46.670
on the cross for you to remain

00:15:46.670 --> 00:15:46.680
sick.'I

00:15:46.680 --> 00:15:50.629
crushed that woman.

00:15:54.440 --> 00:15:57.230
Out of

00:15:57.240 --> 00:16:00.389
trying to be so bold about my

00:16:00.399 --> 00:16:02.870
faith, basically

00:16:02.870 --> 00:16:02.880
what

00:16:02.880 --> 00:16:04.550
I

00:16:04.550 --> 00:16:04.560
was saying

00:16:04.560 --> 00:16:06.629
was

00:16:06.629 --> 00:16:06.639
she

00:16:06.639 --> 00:16:08.629
must not

00:16:08.639 --> 00:16:10.629
have enough faith. I

00:16:10.639 --> 00:16:12.710
was

00:16:12.710 --> 00:16:12.720
in

00:16:12.720 --> 00:16:15.389
my

00:16:15.399 --> 00:16:19.389
early 20s and immature. I'll never forget how I

00:16:19.399 --> 00:16:20.470
crushed that

00:16:20.480 --> 00:16:24.430
woman.

00:16:30.519 --> 00:16:33.550
When Megan got diagnosed three

00:16:33.560 --> 00:16:36.430
or four years later, I walked in her

00:16:36.440 --> 00:16:39.110
office and told her,

00:16:39.120 --> 00:16:40.790
'I owe you a big

00:16:40.800 --> 00:16:44.069
apology. I'm at the bottom of the

00:16:44.079 --> 00:16:46.509
hole.'I've

00:16:46.519 --> 00:16:49.189
had

00:16:49.199 --> 00:16:51.110
people

00:16:51.110 --> 00:16:51.120
tell

00:16:51.120 --> 00:16:52.230
us all the time, 'Your

00:16:52.240 --> 00:16:53.509
daughter has devils; you need to go get

00:16:53.519 --> 00:16:54.910
them cast

00:16:54.910 --> 00:16:54.920
out.'We

00:16:54.920 --> 00:16:58.389
went to deliverance

00:16:58.399 --> 00:17:00.710
services and all kinds of things,

00:17:05.400 --> 00:17:08.630
trying to find a solution to

00:17:08.640 --> 00:17:11.350
autism. That's why I

00:17:11.360 --> 00:17:13.549
have compassion.

00:17:13.559 --> 00:17:16.990
Until you live it, you

00:17:16.990 --> 00:17:17.000
don't know.

00:17:17.000 --> 00:17:19.029
When I

00:17:19.039 --> 00:17:20.350
hear some of the things you're going

00:17:20.360 --> 00:17:23.630
through, I go, 'Brandon,

00:17:23.640 --> 00:17:26.829
shut

00:17:28.909 --> 00:17:28.919
up'compared

00:17:30.960 --> 00:17:32.990
to

00:17:36.679 --> 00:17:38.350
the pain some of you are going through.

00:17:42.400 --> 00:17:44.150
How can you complain when somebody else

00:17:44.160 --> 00:17:47.070
has it so much worse? But

00:17:51.559 --> 00:17:54.909
we have

00:17:54.919 --> 00:17:57.310
compassion for those

00:17:57.320 --> 00:18:01.430
that are hurting.

00:18:06.760 --> 00:18:08.950
You are

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:12.710
warriors. Jesus is so proud of you.

00:18:12.720 --> 00:18:15.990
I believe with all my

00:18:16.000 --> 00:18:19.029
heart there's an expiration date to your

00:18:19.039 --> 00:18:23.149
circumstance, just like ours.

00:18:23.149 --> 00:18:23.159
Hope—that's

00:18:23.159 --> 00:18:26.510
what we do. We always

00:18:26.520 --> 00:18:29.590
put ourselves in hope and say, 'God, we know

00:18:29.600 --> 00:18:31.430
that you will meet us at the point of

00:18:31.440 --> 00:18:34.669
our

00:18:34.669 --> 00:18:34.679
need.'We

00:18:34.679 --> 00:18:36.270
don't know when that day of full

00:18:36.280 --> 00:18:40.350
manifestation is coming, but I believe

00:18:40.350 --> 00:18:40.360
in

00:18:40.360 --> 00:18:44.149
being fully persuaded that what God has

00:18:44.159 --> 00:18:47.590
promised, He is able also to

00:18:47.600 --> 00:18:50.510
perform. Even in the deadness of Sarah's

00:18:50.520 --> 00:18:52.390
womb and

00:18:52.400 --> 00:18:56.110
Abraham's

00:18:56.120 --> 00:18:59.909
old age,

00:18:59.909 --> 00:18:59.919
they

00:18:59.919 --> 00:19:04.390
believed in hope.

00:19:08.200 --> 00:19:11.029
Faith as a grain of a mustard seed,

00:19:11.039 --> 00:19:13.549
the Bible says, will move your mountain.

00:19:21.240 --> 00:19:25.630
I doubt my doubt. Devil, I

00:19:25.640 --> 00:19:29.190
refuse to let this doubt build a

00:19:29.200 --> 00:19:31.510
root inside of me. Out of the abundance of my

00:19:31.520 --> 00:19:33.909
heart, the mouth will speak. I renew my

00:19:33.919 --> 00:19:36.190
mind to what the Lord said I could

00:19:36.200 --> 00:19:39.070
have. I want you to hear this story

00:19:39.080 --> 00:19:40.430
about Katherine

00:19:40.440 --> 00:19:42.950
Kuhlman

00:19:42.960 --> 00:19:45.470
real quick. In the early days of her

00:19:45.480 --> 00:19:47.630
ministry, Katherine was greatly disturbed

00:19:47.640 --> 00:19:49.270
over many things that she observed in

00:19:49.280 --> 00:19:51.630
the field of divine healing. 'I hated

00:19:51.640 --> 00:19:53.750
traditional tent healing

00:19:53.750 --> 00:19:53.760
services,'she

00:19:53.760 --> 00:19:56.029
explained. 'Those long healing lines, the

00:19:56.039 --> 00:19:58.909
filling out of cards—it was an insult to

00:19:58.919 --> 00:20:01.430
your intelligence.'Once, after visiting

00:20:01.440 --> 00:20:03.950
such a service, she cried all night.

00:20:03.950 --> 00:20:03.960
She

00:20:03.960 --> 00:20:05.990
determined that with the Holy Spirit's

00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:09.230
help, her ministry would not be that way.

00:20:13.280 --> 00:20:16.149
She delved

00:20:16.159 --> 00:20:18.990
even harder into the word of God for

00:20:19.000 --> 00:20:22.430
answers. Katherine said, 'Too often I

00:20:22.440 --> 00:20:25.430
had seen pathetically sick people

00:20:25.440 --> 00:20:27.390
dragging their tired, weakened bodies

00:20:27.400 --> 00:20:29.190
home from a healing service,

00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:31.029
having been told that they were not

00:20:31.039 --> 00:20:33.029
healed simply because of their own lack

00:20:33.039 --> 00:20:35.789
of faith.'Her heart ached for these people

00:20:35.799 --> 00:20:38.510
as she knew how they struggled day

00:20:38.520 --> 00:20:40.870
after day, trying desperately to obtain

00:20:40.880 --> 00:20:43.950
more faith,

00:20:43.960 --> 00:20:46.669
trying to analyze

00:20:46.679 --> 00:20:49.549
their

00:20:49.559 --> 00:20:52.230
deficiency.

00:20:55.600 --> 00:20:58.070
They were

00:20:58.070 --> 00:20:58.080
unwittingly

00:20:58.080 --> 00:21:00.669
looking at themselves

00:21:00.679 --> 00:21:04.070
rather than to God. She

00:21:09.760 --> 00:21:12.230
saw

00:21:12.240 --> 00:21:13.909
the harm that was being done in

00:21:13.919 --> 00:21:17.510
attributing everything to lack of faith

00:21:17.520 --> 00:21:19.430
on the part of the individual.

00:21:23.710 --> 00:21:23.720
Kuhlman

00:21:28.000 --> 00:21:31.110
suggested

00:21:31.120 --> 00:21:32.510
that her prayer was answered in the

00:21:32.520 --> 00:21:34.950
spring of 1947 when she began studying

00:21:34.960 --> 00:21:36.909
the Holy

00:21:36.919 --> 00:21:39.029
Spirit. She realized that when the

00:21:39.039 --> 00:21:41.909
crucified Christ said, 'It is

00:21:41.909 --> 00:21:41.919
finished,'He

00:21:41.919 --> 00:21:43.950
included not only the salvation of the

00:21:43.960 --> 00:21:46.310
soul but the healing and deliverance of

00:21:46.320 --> 00:21:48.950
the body as well. Even if

00:21:48.950 --> 00:21:48.960
she

00:21:48.960 --> 00:21:51.310
never saw a single healing

00:21:51.320 --> 00:21:53.830
miracle,

00:21:53.840 --> 00:21:56.149
it would not change

00:21:56.159 --> 00:21:58.789
God's word. The

00:21:58.789 --> 00:21:58.799
secret

00:21:58.799 --> 00:22:01.110
of the

00:22:01.110 --> 00:22:01.120
power

00:22:01.120 --> 00:22:02.990
of

00:22:02.990 --> 00:22:03.000
healing is

00:22:03.000 --> 00:22:06.909
found

00:22:06.909 --> 00:22:06.919
in

00:22:06.919 --> 00:22:10.470
the

00:22:10.480 --> 00:22:13.669
person of the Holy Spirit.

00:22:16.400 --> 00:22:18.549
Katherine

00:22:20.880 --> 00:22:22.630
Kuhlman

00:22:24.799 --> 00:22:27.350
said a reporter once

00:22:27.350 --> 00:22:27.360
asked,

00:22:27.360 --> 00:22:29.470
'How much time do you spend preparing

00:22:29.480 --> 00:22:31.870
for a miracle

00:22:31.880 --> 00:22:34.029
service?'She

00:22:34.039 --> 00:22:36.830
said,

00:22:36.840 --> 00:22:39.830
'I stay

00:22:41.919 --> 00:22:44.789
prepared 24 hours a

00:22:44.789 --> 00:22:44.799
day.'She

00:22:44.799 --> 00:22:47.149
was

00:22:57.919 --> 00:23:00.669
frustrated

00:23:02.480 --> 00:23:06.950
seeing people walk away

00:23:06.960 --> 00:23:10.230
without their miracle.

00:23:22.400 --> 00:23:26.350
Hope deferred makes the heart

00:23:26.360 --> 00:23:29.510
sick.

00:23:34.520 --> 00:23:36.390
You're not

00:23:36.400 --> 00:23:39.029
alone.

00:23:39.039 --> 00:23:41.549
I know you've used a lot of scripture, prayed a

00:23:41.559 --> 00:23:44.590
lot,

00:23:44.590 --> 00:23:44.600
and

00:23:44.600 --> 00:23:47.390
fasted,

00:23:49.000 --> 00:23:51.510
but I believe

00:23:51.520 --> 00:23:53.950
there's an

00:23:53.960 --> 00:23:57.029
expiration date to your

00:23:57.039 --> 00:23:58.870
circumstance. Even if

00:23:58.870 --> 00:23:58.880
people die,

00:23:58.880 --> 00:24:01.350
they

00:24:01.360 --> 00:24:03.029
get

00:24:03.039 --> 00:24:06.350
their miracle on the other

00:24:06.360 --> 00:24:10.750
side. God's not a failure, and you're not a

00:24:10.760 --> 00:24:13.110
failure.

00:24:14.640 --> 00:24:16.110
You

00:24:16.120 --> 00:24:17.789
still have victory

00:24:17.799 --> 00:24:20.230
regardless if you get it on this

00:24:20.240 --> 00:24:21.950
side or the other side.

00:24:25.760 --> 00:24:29.630
I just choose to stay in a place of

00:24:29.640 --> 00:24:33.630
victory.

00:24:48.760 --> 00:24:51.269
I'm not going to

00:24:51.279 --> 00:24:53.110
let my mind

00:24:58.200 --> 00:24:59.389
wander.

00:25:06.440 --> 00:25:08.389
When days like

00:25:08.399 --> 00:25:11.070
that happen, put on worship music and

00:25:11.080 --> 00:25:14.710
rejoice like it's already happened.

00:25:17.720 --> 00:25:20.789
If

00:25:20.799 --> 00:25:23.149
the devil can't steal your joy, he can't

00:25:23.159 --> 00:25:25.669
steal your goods. The Bible says He

00:25:25.669 --> 00:25:25.679
gives

00:25:25.679 --> 00:25:27.470
a garment of praise for a spirit of

00:25:28.870 --> 00:25:28.880
heaviness.

00:25:31.520 --> 00:25:32.990
I just want to encourage you because

00:25:39.200 --> 00:25:41.389
I don't

00:25:41.399 --> 00:25:43.789
want to be

00:25:46.389 --> 00:25:46.399
hyperspiritual.

00:25:49.960 --> 00:25:53.549
I don't

00:25:53.559 --> 00:25:56.630
want to be the

00:25:56.640 --> 00:25:59.470
Hollywood Christian

00:25:59.470 --> 00:25:59.480
where

00:25:59.480 --> 00:26:01.669
everything is okay.

00:26:06.669 --> 00:26:06.679
I've

00:26:11.279 --> 00:26:14.549
got

00:26:14.559 --> 00:26:15.350
my

00:26:15.360 --> 00:26:18.950
stuff.

00:26:18.960 --> 00:26:21.470
Everybody

00:26:21.470 --> 00:26:21.480
has

00:26:21.480 --> 00:26:22.549
something they're going through,

00:26:22.559 --> 00:26:24.070
regardless of how much they try to

00:26:24.080 --> 00:26:25.870
make themselves

00:26:25.870 --> 00:26:25.880
look

00:26:25.880 --> 00:26:27.789
spiritual.

00:26:32.320 --> 00:26:34.310
No matter how big

00:26:34.320 --> 00:26:36.990
the name is,

00:26:37.000 --> 00:26:40.070
they've all got

00:26:40.080 --> 00:26:43.269
issues.

00:26:50.919 --> 00:26:54.470
They put

00:26:54.480 --> 00:26:58.230
their pants on just like I do.

00:27:00.389 --> 00:27:00.399
My

00:27:02.279 --> 00:27:04.430
relationship with God

00:27:33.159 --> 00:27:36.389
was birthed

00:27:36.399 --> 00:27:39.350
out of desperation and pure hell—not being able to read or write, being bullied as a kid

00:27:39.350 --> 00:27:39.360
and

00:27:39.360 --> 00:27:43.389
as a

00:27:43.399 --> 00:27:47.509
janitor.

00:27:49.880 --> 00:27:54.029
Hearing Him was out of

00:27:54.039 --> 00:27:57.310
desperation. That's why I say,

00:27:57.320 --> 00:27:58.950
how bad do you want

00:27:58.960 --> 00:28:02.470
it?

00:28:04.200 --> 00:28:07.149
Every single thing has not ever

00:28:07.159 --> 00:28:09.110
come to me

00:28:09.120 --> 00:28:11.750
easy. There's been things where I've seen

00:28:11.760 --> 00:28:14.870
greater victory than others, but it has come

00:28:14.880 --> 00:28:18.750
out of just being a bulldog on a bone. I

00:28:18.760 --> 00:28:22.350
refuse to give up.

00:28:26.549 --> 00:28:26.559
I'll

00:28:31.200 --> 00:28:33.509
seek Him and I'll find

00:28:33.519 --> 00:28:37.190
Him. I will touch the hem of His

00:28:37.200 --> 00:28:40.590
garment because if I have nothing else, I

00:28:40.600 --> 00:28:43.870
have Him.

00:29:02.519 --> 00:29:05.590
I've had eight visitations from the

00:29:05.600 --> 00:29:08.470
Lord Jesus Christ.

00:29:08.480 --> 00:29:10.669
Does it make me any more special

00:29:10.679 --> 00:29:14.549
than you? No. I seek Him and I

00:29:14.559 --> 00:29:17.350
find

00:29:17.360 --> 00:29:21.070
Him. There's no

00:29:21.080 --> 00:29:23.710
shortcuts. I

00:29:23.720 --> 00:29:27.669
continually

00:29:27.669 --> 00:29:27.679
feed

00:29:27.679 --> 00:29:29.389
my

00:29:29.399 --> 00:29:31.789
faith because I'm

00:29:31.799 --> 00:29:34.389
desperate. I want that little girl to get

00:29:34.399 --> 00:29:38.149
better. I want my family

00:29:38.159 --> 00:29:40.750
restored.

00:29:40.760 --> 00:29:44.230
I want the tangible

00:29:44.240 --> 00:29:47.149
presence of God on my life so

00:29:47.149 --> 00:29:47.159
that when

00:29:47.159 --> 00:29:50.669
I walk into an

00:29:50.679 --> 00:29:53.310
atmosphere, it changes.

00:29:53.320 --> 00:29:55.909
Not to give me glory, but to give Him

00:29:55.919 --> 00:29:58.590
glory.

00:29:58.600 --> 00:30:02.029
Bottom line is, if we get

00:30:02.039 --> 00:30:04.789
this glorious gospel preached

00:30:04.799 --> 00:30:06.710
throughout the whole world, then the end

00:30:06.720 --> 00:30:07.549
will

00:30:07.559 --> 00:30:11.750
come and all the drama of this world is

